readable.content: A boy and a girl are standing near the water on a beach . A girl in a cowboy hat and a boy standing on the ocean shore A young boy and girl posing on the beach . The boy and girl are standing in front of the ocean and mountains . The boy in the gray t-shirt is standing next to the girl in the green dress and cowboy hat on the beach .
